Andy

Reported by Nikos Spanoudakis on the Epsilon newsgroup:
> I had written:
> 
> @spec{
>     MetaModel "SUC"{
>         nsURI: "http://mi.parisdescartes.fr/ASEME/metamodels/SUC"
